10:
Enough yapping. I ain't got all day,
you know.
14:
The matter, kid? All tuckered out
already?
25:
Heh. Looks like you've still got some
juice left in you after all.
36: You know, this is kinda fun!
51:
Phew... I'm pretty parched, now that
you mention it. How'd you know?
54:
You're makin' way too many
unnecessary movements.
60:
In fact, I don't think I've ever seen
anyone move so much with such
little purpose before.
65:
Whoa... I must be some kind of
prodigy then, huh? I knew I was
warrior material!
69: That's NOT what I said. Relax.
77:
Anyway, I already told you. There
ain't much strife between canids
and felines anymore.
78:
So why're you so gung ho about
becoming a warrior?
91:
It's not like I had it out against felines
or anything like that. I mean, you're
my teacher now, right?
95:
But like... warriors and stuff are super
cool, right?
98:
I wanna be the kind of bad-ass that
can protect their friends no matter
what!
103:
You're one happy-go-lucky kid, I'll
give you that.
106:
But sure. I guess we can work with
that for—
115:
Damn... We're surrounded! I can't
believe I didn't sniff them out until
now.
120:
Lou, find somewhere safe to hide! I'll
take care of this one way or another!
125: No way, man! I'm fighting too!
128:
Look, you can prove yourself to me
later, but now—
142:
Don't worry about me—this is
nothing. Just make sure you get
outta here!
160:
I already told you—this is nothing!
See? So just focus on your
surroundings!
168:
Good. Remember your trainng. Eyes
forward, and don't let your guard
down.
173: Eyes forward, guard up. Got it!
176:
Not half bad, kid. You might have it
in you after all!
179:
Now... Are you ready to kick some
ass?
182:
Heck yeah! Let's show these chumps
who's boss!
198: W-we did it! We took 'em all out!
203: Yeah, yeah... Don't get too excited.
204:
But next time, try not to
tunnel-vision too hard, or else you
might find yourself in another
situation where—
208:
Wait, the hell am I explainin' this to
you for, anyway? I'm not your damn
babysitter!
213:
Wahoo! One step closer to
becoming a full-fledged warrior!
We've gotta do this again sometime,
Nimbus!
